  }), mdx("p", null, "I introduced some high-level thoughts on a governance strategy and its importance in the previous post.\nFirst, I want to establish the current governance options available out of the box.\nWe will not dive deeply into these options right now; I\u2019d instead set some of these into context in individual posts at a later time."), mdx("h1", {
