  }, mdx("p", {
    parentName: "li"
  }, mdx("strong", {
    parentName: "p"
  }, "Naming convention"), "\nThen we need to decide if we want naming conventions for our Teams. Naming conventions and a healthy amount of acronyms help understand the team\u2019s purpose. And whenever needed, we could make use of locations as well. Technically, we can use Naming Policies, and Custom Blocked words if we have Azure AD P1. We can also leave it up to the users during creation or tie naming to the templates in a custom provisioning solution. More on this another time.")), mdx("li", {
