  }, mdx("strong", {
    parentName: "p"
  }, "Monitoring"), "\nFrom my point of view, monitoring has multiple purposes. It can involve quantitative monitoring and measuring against KPIs, service health, etc. It could also mean qualitative measuring via workshops and surveys to measure user satisfaction. We have many technical options to measure in the Microsoft 365 suite. We should probably dive into establishing a baseline and continuously measuring progress in another post.")), mdx("li", {
